      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver 414 hp with a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and tactile engagement. This example has been fastidiously maintained with preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators already addressed. The chassis remains sharp, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adjustable damping characteristics for varied road conditions. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its 'good' status, the vehicle's structural integrity and powertrain performance remain uncompromisingly sharp.",
